sets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"262571addd62b631d480de226d16ee5296fbf11c","tid":1862691,"uid":55725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T20:09:22.000Z","msg":"手環會有幾個問題<br />\n1. 防水能力<br />\n如果坐開浴缸，唔知長浸係水入面有幾勁啦，至少要IP67<br />\n2. 防撞能力<br />\n如果唔小心一下轉身撞爆咗，唔知班死黑警上門會唔會打柒你啦<br />\n3. 舒適度<br />\n差，太大舊，正一狗屎垃圾<br />\n4. 抗干擾能力<br />\n呢樣唔講得笑，隔離鄰舍藍芽裝置多就好大機會有干擾，今日先試過microsoft隻老鼠jam撚咗logitech鍵盤，打字lag到核爆<br />\n5. 部電話使唔使用wifi先？要wifi就要多舊魚<br />\n用SIM卡就一個Faraday cage搞惦，班狗屎垃圾死黑警永遠唔知<br />\n<br />\n結婚：狗屎垃圾一大舊"},{"pid":"71258f4fc4e9f5e6be80ffa1117a9f23bd81c37b","tid":1862691,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:04:41.000Z","msg":"如果禁果個人，唔禁同住嘅屋企人，都冇乜意思"},{"pid":"52c7cfe8d779cf3088fd7a3368f615d24b7f66ca","tid":1862691,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71258f4fc4e9f5e6be80ffa1117a9f23bd81c37b","tid":1862691,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:04:41.000Z","msg":"如果禁果個人，唔禁同住嘅屋企人，都冇乜意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:09:23.000Z","msg":"777係鋪路監控新屋嶺/831死者家人, 遭警魔輪姦的女仔全家"},{"pid":"17aa25e6beb267873854a15a2510fb7effc8f959","tid":1862691,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:11:03.000Z","msg":"撥畀醫院好過啦"},{"pid":"f41072d4a401f68e9e7ac789991df6be4c9d4097","tid":1862691,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:15:26.000Z","msg":"用電話咪算囉<br />\n會坐監邊個夠膽走<br />\n又係政治任務黎啦<br />\n成班人渣個屎忽腦永遠諗住點控制人<br />\n酷吏無善終<br />\n死左落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3b2b5128542cba49aa7b48102a9390a8b71630","tid":1862691,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:18:28.000Z","msg":"又會咁啱有呢個工具<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n500個存貨，唔知一年係唔係拉咗500個手足呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e73b96cec265b30171e006b71f8eff21522e05b3","tid":1862691,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbadfa316101f8a7dd36f519f8e39a3879608b3d","tid":1862691,"uid":1251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T19:22:14.000Z","msg":"即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎埋手機出街就可以無憂播毒？<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">手環採用 BLE （藍牙低能耗）技術，與同時派發的手機設備連接起來，有效射程為 20 至 30 米，佩戴者一旦離開處所，手機無法偵測到手環即會自動發送通知知會警方</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T22:18:38.000Z","msg":"個電話有GPS?"}]}